# Habit Tracker Pro v1.0.0

🚀 **First stable release** of the professional habit reporting tool!

## ✨ Key Features
- 📊 CSV to Markdown report conversion
- 🎨 Customizable Jinja2 templates
- ⚡ One-click execution
- 🌍 UTF-8 support for multilingual reports
- 💼 Pro version promotion integration

## ⚙️ System Requirements
- Python 3.8+
- pandas library
- jinja2 library

## ⬇️ Installation
```bash
pip install pandas jinja2
## 🚦 Usage
```bash
python main.py
```

## 📂 Output
- Generated report: `reports/habit_report.md`

